
 "\\#" [1byte operation]
 "\\#" [0x01] [2bytes address] [1byte value] write register
 "\\#" [0x02] [2bytes address] read register
 "\\#" [0x03] [2bytes address] [1byte length] [n byte payload] write multiple registers
 "\\#" [0x04] [2bytes address] [1byte length] read multiple registers

 '\\' characters in the payload are escaped as "\\\\"
